name: Cloud Next Extended 2019
description: This time Google Cloud Developers Community, Indore presents you the most exciting event for May 2019: Cloudnext Extended 2019!  Most awaited event of the year - where we will be reviewing various intriguing cloud technologies introduced at the Google Cloudnext event held at San Francisco.  So get ready to witness some of our expert speakers who will be conducting a variety of sessions on different areas of cloud-related technologies .  Details:  Date: 12 May 2019 Venue: Wittyfeed Headquarters, Shekhar Central, Palasia, Indore Time: 10 AM to 4 PM  Registration: 9-10 Welcome Note: 10:15-10:30 Speaker Sessions Phase 1 : Dharmesh Vaya-> Google Anthos: 10:30-11:30 Rajat Jaiswal-> Business Automation using Microsoft Flow: 11:30-12:30 Lunch : 12:30-1:00 Speaker Sessions Phase 2: Tushar Pal -> Google Cloud Run: 1:00-2:00 Akash Agrawal -> Kubernetes and ML: 2:00-3:00 Panel discussion: 3:00-3:30 Closing Note Networking  Register here: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/cloud-next-extended-19-tickets-60827713328  For any questions please E-Mail us at gcdcindore@gmail.com
